Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar mai cike da zargi da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da matarsa Christine Blasey Ford a kan wasu laifuffukan fyade da aka yi masa a shekarun 1980 a tashoshin talabijin shida a ranar Alhamis.
A daidai wannan lokacin, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba da ci gaba, inda kafofin watsa labarai suka dakatar da shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don ɗaukar juzu'i na ƙarshe a ranar Juma'a: Sanatan Arizona Jeff Flake ya ba da kwangilar FBI don gudanar da binciken mako guda na zargin.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a cewa ya tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa wata mugun rauni a kan kansa a lokacin da yake bugu kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafin matarsa a bikin kammala karatun sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin furcinsa na sha'awar cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli shirin a ranar Jumma'a, in ji rahoton Nielsen.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin masu kallo a tashoshin talabijin na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu lambobin da aka ba da dama ba a kan sauran tashoshin da suka nuna shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen lissafin yawan mutanen da ke kallon shirye-shiryen a hukumomi.
Idan aka gwada, wannan adadi ya yi daidai da na 'yan wasan da ke halartar gasar kofin kwallon kafa ko kuma na waɗanda suke halartar gasar Oscar.
Shugabannin ra'ayi a Fox News Channel, wadanda suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, sun jagoranci dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa a cikin taron da ya dauki tsawon rana daya wanda ya kai kimanin masu kallo miliyan 5.69, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta zo ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.1, NBC miliyan 2.94, MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52, Nielsen ya ce.
Amma bayan shari'ar, mutane sun ci gaba da son wannan littafin.
Flake ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin mai matsakaicin jam'iyyar Republican ya bayyana cewa zai kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama mutumin a safiyar ranar Juma'a bayan da masu zanga-zangar suka yi masa tsawa, yana kokarin hawa lif zuwa taron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya a ƙasa na mintuna da yawa lokacin da aka zarge shi kuma aka watsa shi kai tsaye a CNN.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
Kuna ganin zai gaya wa ƙasar gaskiya?
Sai aka ce mata, "Kai mai iko ne, alhali kuwa mata da yawa ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce sashen sa ya fitar da wata sanarwa, ya kuma ce kafin a rufe lif din, yana da wasu abubuwa da zai faɗa a taron kwamitin shari'a.
Kafofin watsa labarai da na talabijin sun watsa shirye-shiryen ne sa'o'i da dama bayan da kwamitin shari'a ya kada kuri'ar turawa majalisar dattijai takardar nadin Kavanaugh.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai a kan cewa FBI za ta fara binciken tuhumar da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, wanda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Wani abokinsa ɗan majalisar dattijai mai suna Chris Coons ne ya sa Flake ya yi hakan.
Bayan tattaunawar da aka yi da Coons da sauran sanatoci, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Flake ya yanke hukunci mai tasiri, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su iya samun kuri'un Kavanaugh ba tare da tabbatar da binciken ba.
