Jaridar ta ce an yi wa mutane 14 da suka ji rauni a zanga-zangar magani.
An ci gaba da samun tashin hankali a yankin bayan shekara guda da Madrid ta ayyana zaben raba gardama da aka yi a ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba a matsayin wanda ba bisa ka'ida ba, amma duk da haka Catalans masu son raba gari sun yi murna.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun kada kuri'ar neman 'yancin kai, duk da cewa yawan masu kada kuri'ar sun yi kasala saboda masu adawa da ficewar sun yi watsi da kuri'ar.
