Ko da yake ma'aikatan World Vision daga Donggala sun isa birnin Palu lafiya, inda suka sami mafaka a cikin allunan kyauta da aka kafa a farfajiyar ofishinsu, sun ga abubuwa masu ban tsoro a hanyarsu, in ji Mr. Doseba.
"Sun ce sun ga gidaje da dama da suka lalace", in ji shi.
Wannan mummunan abu ne.
Duk da yadda sojojin agaji suka fara aikin rage radadin bala'in, wasu sun yi korafin cewa an hana ma'aikatan kungiyoyin agaji na kasashen waje da suka kware zuwa Palus.
