Taron yakin neman zaben Trump a jihar West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara jerin shirye-shiryen yakin neman zabensa a wannan karon a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko cikin biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran a yanke hukuncin tabbatar da shi, har sai Trump ya zabi wanda zai nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, yana kokarin kara yawan goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron neman zaben Trump a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a Intanet?
Taron yakin neman zaben Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia zai gudana a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 da karfe 7 na yamma agogon Gabas.
Za a iya kallon taron yakin neman zaben Trump a jihar West Virginia a yanar gizo ta hanyar YouTube.
Ana ganin Trump yana magana ne game da sauraron shari'ar da aka yi a wannan makon game da zargin cin zarafin mata da maza, yayin da majalisar dattijai ta dakatar da zaben a cikin mako guda, yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma babban manufar wannan jerin abubuwan yakin neman zabe shine don taimakawa Republican su sake samun kwarin gwiwa yayin da suke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Shugaban yakin neman zaben na Shugaba Trump ya ce taron na mako biyar da ke tafe zai nuna masu son sa kai da masu goyon bayansa a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shugaban kasa, don haka Trump yana tafiya cikin sauri a lokacin yakin neman zabe, yana shiga jihohi da dama", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda bai so a bayyana sunansa ba.
Taron yakin neman zabe da za a yi a gidan wasan Wesbanco da ke Wheeling zai iya jawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma za a samu rahoto daga kafofin yada labarai a Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
Wannan shine ziyarar Trump ta biyu a jihar West Virginia a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un masu jefa kuri'a a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican daga jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya jagoranci zaben shugaban kasa.
"Wannan ba kyakkyawan labari ba ne ga Morseys cewa shugaban ya zo ya karfafa sakamakon nasa", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, Reuters ta ruwaito.
