Turai ne a kan Ryder Cup karshe rana 106 ya jagoranci
Turai za ta samu ci gaba a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup, inda ta ci gaba da kasancewa a saman Amurka da ci 10 da 6 bayan wasannin hudu da wasannin biyu da aka yi a ranar Asabar.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun yi nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods, wanda ke fama da rashin lafiya, don kara yawan maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National.
Thomas Bjorn, dan wasan Turai wanda ya yi kokarin ceto kofin da ya rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya yi nasara a wasan da ya yi da Amurka bayan da suka yi kasa a raga hudu da safe, inda suka ci wasan 3-1.
