Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna haske na yau da kullum, amma yanzu ya rasa 29 daga cikin hudu da kuma 19 daga cikin wasanni bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta da safiya don buga kwallo hudu, ya dawo tare da abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a wasan biyu, inda ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da 2-1 - na farko da na uku a duniya.
