China ta ba da rahoton cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ce fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suke fama da wannan ciwo.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin shari'o'in sun samo asali ne daga jima'i, suna canja abin da ya gabata.
A wasu sassan kasar Sin, cutar HIV ta fi yaduwa ta hanyar daukar kwayar cutar ta jini.
Amma, a wannan hanyar, an rage yawan mutanen da ke da cutar zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
A kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau a China yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar kanjamau ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT a China.
An halatta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma an ce an nuna bambanci sosai ga mutanen LGBT.
Domin al'adar ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suka yi jima'i da maza suna aure.
Yawancin cututtuka suna da nasaba da rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin irin waɗannan dangantaka.
