Amurka za ta iya amfani da dakarun ruwan ta wajen hana Rasha fitar da makamashi - ministan cikin gida
A cewar jaridar Washington Examiner, Washington na iya amfani da sojan ruwanta idan ya cancanta don hana Rasha shiga kasuwar makamashi, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke.
Zinke ya ce, shigar Rasha cikin Syria, musamman idan ta yi aiki a kan gayyatar gwamnati, wata hujja ce ta binciken sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine suna son su kawo makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, a cikin kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma jami'in ya ce akwai hanyoyin da kuma kayan aiki don magance wannan.
Amurka tana da wannan damar ta hanyar sojin ruwanmu don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku suna budewa kuma idan ya cancanta, an toshe su don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba zai shiga kasuwa ba,' in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ne ga masu halartar taron da kungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke tunkarar Rasha da Iran, ya ce sun yi kama.
"Iraniya da Rasha za su zabi tattalin arziki, da yawa ko kadan, don bunkasa da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake mai da hankali kan Rasha a matsayin "wannan doki mai dabara daya" wanda tattalin arzikinsa ya dogara da burbushin mai.
Wannan sanarwa ta zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke da burin kara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta yi watsi da "kwarewar" da ba ta dace ba game da aikin bututun Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya mayar da Berlin "kurkuku" ga Moscow.
