Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, inda suka kara da cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu na karuwa.
Tun da babu sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su samu wani bayani daga Donggala Regency da ke arewacin Palau ba, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An bukaci a kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga wurin.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kusa da wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma an kiyasta yawan jama'arsa a shekara ta 2017 ya kai 379,800.
A lokacin da birnin yake bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafawarsa, wata girgizar ƙasa da tsunami ta auku.
Donggala Regency yanki ne da ke nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekarar 2017, an kiyasta yawan mazaunan garin Regens, wanda ke ƙarƙashin yankin lardin, ya kai 299 200.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki a lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar nickel yana da muhimmanci a lardin, wanda ya fi mayar da hankali ga Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i a ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi tsunami a yankunan Palau da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya auku a Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya auku a yammacin Donggala, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin Tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: A watan Maris da farkon Afrilu, manyan girgizar ƙasa da yawa sun auku a gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya haddasa tsunami da ya auku a kudancin tsibirin kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa yankin da ke kusa da birnin Padanang, a lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke Sumatra, kuma hakan ya haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa Acehi a Pidie Jaya, ta haddasa bala'i da firgici, ta tunatar da mutane game da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka faru a 2004.
Amma, mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a cikin gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa da ta fi ƙarfin ta auku a tsibirin Lombok, a ƙasar Indonesiya, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin a kan zargin cin zarafin da ake yi masa a gida
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da hannu a harin.
Rahoton da 'yan sandan jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar ya nuna cewa an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, a Wasilla, jihar Alaska, bisa zargin yin amfani da wutar lantarki a gida, da kuma sa baki a rahoton tashin hankali da kuma tsayayya wa kama.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa, lokacin da wata mata ta yi ƙoƙarin sanar da 'yan sanda game da zargin aikata laifi, Palin ya ɗauki wayar ta.
An tsare Palin a gidan yari na Mat-Su kuma an ba shi belin da bai kai dala 500 ba, in ji hukumar tsaro ta KTU.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana cewa ba shi da laifi a kowane hali, in ji wata kafar yada labarai ta BBC.
