An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda ake iya yankewa da hukuncin daurin kwana daya da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
A wani labarin da aka yi cewa an kai hari, 'yar'uwarsa Sarah Palin ce aka kira.
Yanzu haka ana shari'ar ne a kotun tsaron Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin gida, da shiga tsakani da rahoton aikata laifukan tashin hankali a gida, da kuma mallakar bindiga, duk a cikin halin bugu.
Abokinta ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
