Sabon bayani game da ruwa: raguwa a Pinellas, Manatees da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka bayar kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobin Florida (FWC) ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan teku a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
FWC ta ce an samu rahotannin karin ci gaba a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar yawan kwayoyin.
